    dataoct_diff[i]=list(range(len(dataoct_diff)))
    dataoct_diff[i][0]=dataoct_diff[j][0]-l
    for k in range(0,len(dataoct_diff)-1):
        dataoct_diff[i][k+1]=dataoct_diff[j][k+1]-dataoct_diff[j][k]

new_cols=["Daily_Confirmed_Diff","Total_Confirmed_Diff","Daily_Recovered_Diff","Total_Recovered_Diff","Daily_Deceased_Diff","Total_Deceased_diff"]
pos_neg_dict={}
pos_neg_len_dict={}
a=[]
b=[]
for i,j in zip(kys,new_cols):
    pos=dataoct_diff[dataoct_diff[j]>0]
    a.append(pos)
    b.append(len(pos))
    neg=dataoct_diff[dataoct_diff[j]<0]
    a.append(neg)
    b.append(len(neg))
    zro=dataoct_diff[dataoct_diff[j]==0]
    a.append(zro)
    b.append(len(zro))
    pos_neg_dict.update({i:a})
    pos_neg_len_dict.update({i:b})
    a=[]
    b=[]

existing_cols
prv_vals=[86748,6310275,85274,5269989,1179,98122]
for i,j,l in zip(new_cols,existing_cols,prv_vals):
    dataoct_ratio_with_precision[i]=list(range(len(dataoct_ratio_with_precision)))
    dataoct_ratio_with_precision[i][0]=round(dataoct_ratio_with_precision[j][0]/l,2)

    dataoct_ratio_with_precision[i]=tmp

    a.append(neg)
    b.append(len(neg))
    zro=dataoct_ratio[dataoct_ratio[j]==0]
    a.append(zro)
    b.append(len(zro))
    one_zro_dict.update({i:a})
    one_zro_len_dict.update({i:b})
    a=[]
    b=[]
